38 //
39 // Class for relative state computed between two PositionVelocity states.
40 //
41 // NOTE! Because this is a relative state, we do NOT support
42 // sampling or configuration space conversions.
43 //
45 
46 #ifndef FASTRACK_STATE_POSITION_VELOCITY_REL_POSITION_VELOCITY_H
47 #define FASTRACK_STATE_POSITION_VELOCITY_REL_POSITION_VELOCITY_H
48 
49 #include <fastrack/state/position_velocity.h>
50 #include <fastrack/state/relative_state.h>
51 
52 namespace fastrack {
53 namespace state {
54 
55 class PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity
56  : public RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PositionVelocity> {
57 public:
58  ~PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity() {}
59 
60  // NOTE! We do NOT provide a default constructor. Objects from this
61  // class SHOULD be initialized from the two corresponding states.
62  explicit PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity(
63  const PositionVelocity &tracker_x, const PositionVelocity &planner_x)
64  : RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PositionVelocity>(),
65  x_(tracker_x.Position() - planner_x.Position(),
66  tracker_x.Velocity() - planner_x.Velocity()) {}
67 
68  // Construct from a PositionVelocity, or from separate position
69  // and velocity vectors.
70  explicit PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity(const PositionVelocity &other)
71  : RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PositionVelocity>(), x_(other) {}
72  explicit PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity(const Vector3d &position,
73  const Vector3d &velocity)
74  : RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PositionVelocity>(),
75  x_(position, velocity) {}
76 
77  // Construct from VectorXd.
78  explicit PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity(const VectorXd &x)
79  : RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PositionVelocity>(), x_(x) {}
80 
81  // Convert from/to VectorXd.
82  void FromVector(const VectorXd& x) { x_.FromVector(x); }
83  VectorXd ToVector() const { return x_.ToVector(); }
84 
85  // Dimension of the state space.
86  static constexpr size_t StateDimension() { return 6; }
87 
88  // Accessors.
89  inline const PositionVelocity &State() const { return x_; }
90 
91 private:
92  // Relative state is just a single PositionVelocity.
93  PositionVelocity x_;
94 }; //\class PositionVelocityRelPositionVelocity

96 } // namespace state
97 } // namespace fastrack
